IMAPAccount amazon
Host ballard.amazon.com
Port 1993
User enrikes
PassCmd "pass outlook.office365.com/enrikes@amazon.com"
SSLType IMAPS
Timeout 120

IMAPStore amazon-remote
Account amazon

MaildirStore amazon-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.Mail/amazon/
Inbox ~/.Mail/amazon/Inbox

Channel amazon
Far :amazon-remote:
Near :amazon-local:
Patterns *
CopyArrivalDate yes
Create Both
SyncState *
Sync All
Expunge Both